title: REVLON Colorburst Lip Butter, Sugar Frosting, 0.09 Ounce
description: Color burst lip butter combines beautiful color with a buttery balm to give you baby soft, healthy glowing lips. It has a pampering gel formula which glides on lips buttery smooth and instantly hydrates lips.

title: OPI The Amazing New Spider-Man Collection, Just Spotted The Lizard
description: OPI's new Spider-Man collection was a bit of an unexpected surprise for me. A comic book themed collection?? For real? That's AWESOME. Okay, not exactly based on comic books, but it was created to coincide with the release of the new 3D Spiderman movie, The Amazing Spider-man, that's coming out in July, so close enough. Still Spiderman. The collection consists of six colors plus a new shade of OPI Shatter crackle
